if was disqualified from last year's world championships after they failed gender eligibility testing.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9990320678462364, \"rank\": 0.0009509402389934359, \"text\": \"Taipei\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taipei\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's world championships\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility testing\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, they were cleared to compete in Paris, setting the stage for one of the biggest controversies of the Games.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995823697835, \"rank\": 4.1763038122709437e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest controversies\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}]}]}"